Verifying your identity, access, privileges assigned and relationship with us for using the Application.
to provide access to content and maintain the Application.
to provide personalized content and recommendations on the basis of your interests and needs
For the purposes of our internal record keeping
Support to law enforcement agencies or in connection with an investigation on matters related 
